text.div:
PublishingModelType

To identify the medium/media in which the cited article is published, eg print, electronic or print-electronic.

This code system http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/publishing-model-type defines the following codes:

Code Display Definition
Print Print Journal in print only (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#article).
Print-Electronic Print-Electronic Journal in print and electronic formats (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#article).
Electronic Electronic Journal in electronic format only (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#article).
Eletronic-eCollection Eletronic-eCollection Electronic-only journal that publishes individual articles then later collects with issue date (see https://www.nlm.nih.gov/bsd/licensee/elements_descriptions.html#article).
